verbose_text: Note that compared to their high expression at the CSB angle, Hs2st is expressed at much lower levels in lateral telencephalon (XREF_FIG A) and Hs6st1 is expressed at much lower levels in the area marked with a cross in XREF_FIG B. There is no gross difference in Fgf8 mRNA distribution between WT, Hs2st -/-, or Hs6st1 -/- CSB (XREF_FIG C-E), indicating any differences in Fgf8 protein distribution between genotypes stems from post-transcriptional regulation.
